<h4 id="what-the-crap-of-openml">what the crap of openml</h4>

<p>An automated machine learning environment.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">openml</span>

